 Anomaly alerts and notifications.
 Polls backend endpoints for telemetry updates.

Example (HTML/JS):

```html
<script src="script.js"></script>
<div id="chart"></div>
<div id="alerts"></div>
```

**script.js** polls `/api/stream` and updates charts dynamically.

