 9. Challenges and Solutions

OneDrive file locks: Moved project outside OneDrive.
Data privacy: Simulated data used; real deployment must comply with HIPAA/GDPR.
Model accuracy: Use more data and fine-tune contamination parameter.
Scalability: Backend designed to handle multiple simultaneous users.

